---
/**
 * Three observability layers described in docs; settings keys from cadence API telemetry metadata.
 */
---

<div class="diagram-wrap">
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    viewBox="0 0 400 168"
    role="img"
    aria-labelledby="ob-title ob-desc"
    class="diagram-svg"
  >
    <title id="ob-title">Observability layers</title>
    <desc id="ob-desc">
      Structured logs on stdout, health endpoints for probes, optional OpenTelemetry export via
      OTLP.
    </desc>
    <rect
      x="12"
      y="8"
      width="376"
      height="44"
      rx="6"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.07"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="1"></rect>
    <text
      x="200"
      y="30"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="11"
      font-weight="600"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
    >
      Structured logs (stdout)
    </text>
    <text
      x="200"
      y="46"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="9"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.82"
    >
      CADENCE_LOG_FORMAT=json
    </text>
    <rect
      x="12"
      y="62"
      width="376"
      height="44"
      rx="6"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.06"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="1"></rect>
    <text
      x="200"
      y="84"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="11"
      font-weight="600"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
    >
      Health &amp; pool endpoints
    </text>
    <text
      x="200"
      y="100"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="9"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.82"
    >
      /health, admin pool stats (see Monitoring guide)
    </text>
    <rect
      x="12"
      y="116"
      width="376"
      height="44"
      rx="6"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.06"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="1"
      stroke-dasharray="4 2"></rect>
    <text
      x="200"
      y="138"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="11"
      font-weight="600"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
    >
      OpenTelemetry (optional)
    </text>
    <text
      x="200"
      y="154"
      text-anchor="middle"
      font-size="9"
      font-family="var(--sl-font, system-ui)"
      fill="currentColor"
      fill-opacity="0.82"
    >
      otel.* via admin APIs → OTLP
    </text>
  </svg>
  <p class="diagram-caption">
    Implementation references: <code>cadence.api.telemetry</code> metadata keys,
    <code>cadence.api.health.router</code>, logging setup in app entry.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  @layer starlight.components {
    .diagram-wrap {
      color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
      margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .diagram-svg {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 30rem;
      height: auto;
    }

    .diagram-caption {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      font-size: var(--sl-text-sm);
      color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
      max-width: 34rem;
    }

    .diagram-caption code {
      font-size: 0.92em;
    }
  }
</style>
